  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were members of the secret police, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was soon after-- soon after that the ghetto proclamation came in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the whole thing had to be found out and the matter became-- it came off the agenda, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If we would have continued to be providing meals there and congregating in that same place month after month and month after month, most probably their interest would have sharpened and the insinuations about how-- about what they would have liked to-- to-- to put onto us all or-- or-- or stick to our backs, so to speak, would have been harder to refute because it was an uneven argument.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a very uneven argument between-- between the secret police in war-time time situation and helpless refugees who live by the grace of those-- of those occupying forces.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyhow, but when we-- coming back to the ghetto and there is a connection in that respect, the-- the-- the-- there were people-- a special Japanese office controlling the ghetto and the-- the-- the coming and going in and out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People that given permission to go out to work from the ghetto for set number of hours a day, but they had to get back-- was closed at 6 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They all had to be in, like a-- a medieval city and the gates were shut closed at a certain time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people used to find nominal employment with-- with-- with the Jewish people or the Chinese people, whoever it is, and so that they could go out [INAUDIBLE] and make some-- something to help them in their daily struggle.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but the people-- the two people who were governing that entire system, one of them was named [?",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
